reviewText: Good class, takes you through sun salutations. The more advances segment may require more upper arm strength than a beginner possesses. Do as many as you can. You will build up to it!

I've been doing yoga for over 10 years and have taken many different styles of yoga.  I love ashtanga yoga, but this dvd literally only has flow sequences (sun salutations a and b, specifically).  Not other poses at all.  I was looking for an ashtanga dvd that is like an asthange class, some flows at the beginning, but then series of other poses and stretches as well.  This only has sun salutations on it, which I can my self at home.
this video helps the beginner or a person returning to the practice of Yoga.  Very worthwhile
